style.color: function(f) {var af = f.get('AF'); af = af.values[0];  if (af < 0.05) {return 'gold';} return 'green';}

onClick.label:

(')} else {neweff=eff;} ;return 'Location: '+start+'
Frequency: '+af+'
Predicted effect:
'+neweff;}
